('Facility Maintenence Technician', 'Mid Level', 'Ohio', 'Yellow Springs', 'As the Facility Maintenance Technician, you will ensure the facility is maintained in a satisfactory condition for all required production and manufacturing operations.', 'The maintenance technician is responsible for the upkeep of the facility and should have a variety of skills, such as plumbing, electrical, carpentry and HVAC certification', 'Mid Level, Cresco'),
