('QC Chemist', 'Mid Level', 'Ohio', 'Yellow Springs', 'The chemist will be responsible for testing equipment as well as assisting in the extraction process of medicinal cannabis. The chemist will test samples for identification, purity, and contaminants.', 'Bachelor’s Degree in chemistry or related field with 1-2 years HPLC experience', 'Mid Level, Cresco'),
